g.text: Acknowledgments
We are grateful to the numerous industry members, state Government staff and volunteers
that have assisted with collecting biological and fisheries data over the years. In particular we
would like to thank Peter Hawthorne, Andrew Hogg and Doug Graske for their efforts collect-
ing catch sampling data and Kylie Odgers (South Australian Research and Development Insti-
tute (SARDI)) for her assistance with entering catch and effort information relevant to the
South Australian Rock Lobster Fishery. We also thank Jonathan Carroll (SARDI) for advice
relating to R statistical procedures, and Ana Redondo Rodriguez (SARDI) for her assistance
with downloading sea-surface temperature data that was sourced fromthe Integrated Marine
Observing System(IMOS) (
http://imos.org.au/
) through the Australian Ocean Data Network
https://portal.aodn.org.au/
). IMOS is a national collaborative research infrastructure, sup-
ported by the Australian Government.
